DarkMouse::

She opened un her link. "Yeah to the conquering heros," she sent to 
the Destrons. "What's up you guys? Grab yourselves a CR and some 
energon and kick back. Our illustrious leader will be with you 
shortly."  She said and closed the link.  For once, she liked her 
desk job. 


--- In nbwrpg@y..., Alloran2@a... wrote:
> OOC: Will someone respond to the Destrons?  We came to the 
Blackfortress, to 
> discuss an alliance, but no one is listening.
> 
> :::Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian:::
> 
> ::Starscream's jaw drops.  he rubs his eyes to make sure he isnt 
dreaming.  
> Bludgeon and Obsidian are just as amazed::
> Starscream: KITKAT?! HOW?
> Bludgeon: how is the question. Ive seen people come back form the 
dead 
> before, but i didnt think it would be possible here.
> Obsidian: Quit questioning Bludgeon, the point is, our Kitkat has 
returned!
> ::Starscream follows Drillbit::
> Starscream: What is it you want to talk with about? And.... how?
